== 赞同 ==
在2000年，他收到由[[美国国家黑人记者协会|美国国家黑人记者协会]]颁发的[[珀西·戈博扎奖|珀西·戈博扎奖]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nabj.org/?page=pastspecial |title=Past Special Honors Recipients |publisher=National Association of Black Journalists |accessdate=5 August 2012 |archive-date=2018-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517011047/http://www.nabj.org/?page=pastspecial |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2006年，他获得了由诺斯科特帕金森基金颁发的[[公民勇气奖|公民勇气奖]]赞扬他"坚决抵抗邪恶而承受的巨大的个人风险".<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.civilcourageprize.org/about-prize.htm |title=Civil Courage Prize |year=2010 |publisher=civilcourageprize.org |accessdate=11 May 2011 |archive-date=2012-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119205933/http://www.civilcourageprize.org/about-prize.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2015年马克斯获得了[[自由表达奖|自由表达奖]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/kerryadolan/2015/03/18/angolan-journalist-rafael-marques-de-morais-wins-freedom-of-expression-award-days-ahead-of-defamation-trial-in-luanda/ |title=Angolan Journalist Rafael Marques De Morais Wins Freedom Of Expression Award Days Ahead Of Defamation Trial In Luanda |year=2015 |publisher=Forbes.com |accessdate=25 March 2015 |archive-date=2020-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013232815/https://www.forbes.com/sites/kerryadolan/2015/03/18/angolan-journalist-rafael-marques-de-morais-wins-freedom-of-expression-award-days-ahead-of-defamation-trial-in-luanda/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

2015年10月1日，拉斐尔·马克斯·德莫赖斯被宣布为2015年阿拉德奖的接收方;与共同获得者John Githongo分享10万加元.<ref>{{cite web|title=Rafael Marques De Morais & John Githongo|url=http://www.allardprize.org/recipient-and-honourable-mentions/rafael-marques-de-morais-john-githongo|website=Allard Prize for International Integrity|publisher=Peter A. Allard School of Law|accessdate=2 October 2015|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123170517/https://www.allardprize.org/recipient-and-honourable-mentions/rafael-marques-de-morais-john-githongo|dead-url=no}}</ref>在谈到他的提名时，马克斯说：“在我面临当局对我的隔离和骚扰的压力时，这是对我工作很大的一个激励。这次提名对于安哥拉中相信腐败是一种刑事犯罪而且是严重的祸害，揭露这种问题是十分重要的市民们提供了希望的曙光。”<ref>{{cite web|title=Rafael Marques De Morais: Allard Prize Finalist|url=http://www.allardprize.org/rafael-marques-de-morais-allard-prize-finalist|website=Allard Prize for International Integrity|publisher=Peter A. Allard School of Law|accessdate=7 August 2015|archive-date=2018-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181006075438/http://www.allardprize.org/rafael-marques-de-morais-allard-prize-finalist|dead-url=no}}</ref>

